@section('main')

    <h1 class="uppercase tracking-wide font-bold text-gray-600">Podcasts</h1>

    <p class="mt-6">Find out about the software development podcast I co-host as well as the podcasts I've made a guest appearance on.</p>

    <div class="mt-6 md:flex md:space-x-6 p-6 bg-white rounded-md shadow-md">
        <img class="flex-shrink-0 w-48 h-48 border" src="https://basecodefieldguide.com/podcast/assets/img/logo.png" />
        <div class="mt-6 md:mt-0 markdown">
            <h2>BaseCode Podcast</h2>
            <p>In 2018 I teamed up with <a href="https://jasonmccreary.me">Jason McCreary</a>, aka JMac (of <a href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Laracon+Jason+McCreary" target="_blank">Laracon</a> and <a href="https://laravelshift.com" target="_blank">Laravel Shift</a> fame) to start the BaseCode Podcast.</p>
            <p>So far we've released 4 mini series, covering the following topics:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>10 practices for writing more readable code</li>
                <li>Automated testing</li>
                <li>Running a SaaS</li>
                <li>Writing idomatic Laravel code</li>
            </ul>

            <p>Check out <a href="https://basecodefieldguide.com/podcast" target="_blank">our website</a> and find us on most podcast platforms!</p>

